trans-unit.source: Represents session-state data for a session store.
trans-unit.target: Representerer økttilstanden data for en økt-butikk.

trans-unit.source: The SessionStateStoreData class is used by ASP.NET and implementers of a custom session-state store to pass session-state information to and from the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateModule>.
trans-unit.target: Klassen SessionStateStoreData brukes til å sende status for økten informasjon til og fra <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateModule>.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateModule> i ASP.NET og implementerere av en egendefinert status for økten store

trans-unit.source: The SessionStateStoreData class is used to represent session-state data for a session store to the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateModule>.
trans-unit.target: Klassen SessionStateStoreData brukes til å vise status for økten data for en økt-butikk til <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateModule>.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateModule>

trans-unit.source: The SessionStateStoreData object contains the session-state variable names and values, static object references, and <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreData.Timeout%2A> information for the current session.
trans-unit.target: SessionStateStoreData objektet inneholder status for økten variabelnavn og verdier, statiske objektreferanser og <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreData.Timeout%2A>informasjon for den gjeldende økten.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreData.Timeout%2A>

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreData"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreData"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreData> class is used to represent session-state data for a session store to the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateModule>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreData>Klassen brukes til å vise status for økten data for en økt butikk til <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateModule>.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateModule> </xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreData>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreData> object contains the session-state variable names and values, static object references, and <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreData.Timeout%2A> information for the current session.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreData>objektet inneholder status for økten variabelnavn og verdier, statiske objektreferanser og <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreData.Timeout%2A>informasjon for den gjeldende økten.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreData.Timeout%2A> </xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreData>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreData> class is used by ASP.NET and implementers of a custom session-state store to pass session-state information to and from the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateModule>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreData>Klassen brukes av ASP.NET og implementerere av en egendefinert status for økten store til å sende status for økten informasjon til og fra <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateModule>.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateModule> </xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreData>

trans-unit.source: Custom session-store implementers construct a <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreData> object in implementations of the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreProviderBase.GetItem%2A>, <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreProviderBase.GetItemExclusive%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreProviderBase.CreateNewStoreData%2A> methods.
trans-unit.target: Egendefinert økt-butikken implementers konstruksjon en <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreData>objektet i implementeringer av den <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreProviderBase.GetItem%2A>, <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreProviderBase.GetItemExclusive%2A>, og <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreProviderBase.CreateNewStoreData%2A>metoder.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreProviderBase.CreateNewStoreData%2A> </xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreProviderBase.GetItemExclusive%2A> </xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreProviderBase.GetItem%2A> </xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreData>

trans-unit.source: The session variables and values for the current session.
trans-unit.target: Økten variablene og verdier for den gjeldende økten.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.HttpStaticObjectsCollection"></xref> for the current session.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.HttpStaticObjectsCollection"> </xref> for gjeldende økt.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreData.Timeout*> for the current session.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreData.Timeout*>for gjeldende økt.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreData.Timeout*>

trans-unit.source: The session variables and values for the current session.
trans-unit.target: Økten variablene og verdier for den gjeldende økten.

trans-unit.source: The Items property references the session-state variables that are exposed to ASP.NET application code using the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionState> class, which is accessed using the <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Session%2A> property of the current <xref:System.Web.HttpContext> or the <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> instance.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen elementer Refererer til status for økten variabler som vises for ASP.NET programmet kode ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionState>klassen som er tilgjengelig via den <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Session%2A>for gjeldende <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>eller <xref:System.Web.UI.Page>forekomsten.</xref:System.Web.UI.Page> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Session%2A> </xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionState>

trans-unit.source: By default, session-state variables are managed using the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection> object.
trans-unit.target: Som standard administreres status for økten variabler med det <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection>objektet.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection>

trans-unit.source: Custom session-store implementers can supply their own implementation of the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection> interface.
trans-unit.target: Egendefinert økt-butikken implementers kan angi sitt eget implementering av den <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection>grensesnittet.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection"></xref> object that contains variables and values for the current session.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection"> </xref> objekt som inneholder verdiene og variabler for gjeldende økt.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of objects declared by <xref uid="langword_csharp_<object Runat="Server" Scope="Session"/>" name="<object Runat="Server" Scope="Session"/>" href=""></xref> tags within the ASP.NET application file Global.asax.
trans-unit.target: Henter en samling objekter som er deklarert med <xref uid="langword_csharp_<object Runat="Server" Scope="Session"/>" name="<object Runat="Server" Scope="Session"/>" href=""> </xref> koder i ASP.NET-programmet filen Global.asax.

trans-unit.source: The StaticObjects property is provided for compatibility with earlier versions of ASP.
trans-unit.target: StaticObjects-egenskapen er angitt for kompatibilitet med tidligere versjoner av ASP.

trans-unit.source: Custom session-store implementers can obtain a reference to the <xref:System.Web.HttpStaticObjectsCollection> class for the current <xref:System.Web.HttpContext> instance using the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateUtility.GetSessionStaticObjects%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Egendefinert økt-butikken implementers kan få en referanse til det <xref:System.Web.HttpStaticObjectsCollection>klasse for gjeldende <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>forekomst ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateUtility.GetSessionStaticObjects%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateUtility.GetSessionStaticObjects%2A> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext> </xref:System.Web.HttpStaticObjectsCollection>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Custom objects stored in the StaticObjects collection must support binary serialization.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Egendefinerte objekter som er lagret i StaticObjects-samlingen må støtte binær Serialiseringsfeil.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Binary Serialization](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [binær serialiseringsfeil](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Web.HttpStaticObjectsCollection"></xref> containing objects declared in the Global.asax file.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.HttpStaticObjectsCollection"> </xref> som inneholder objekter som er deklarert i filen Global.asax.

trans-unit.source: Gets and sets the amount of time, in minutes, allowed between requests before the session-state provider terminates the session.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir hvor lang tid, i minutter, tillatt mellom forespørsler før leverandøren status for økten avsluttes økten.

trans-unit.source: The time-out period in minutes.
trans-unit.target: Tidsavbruddperioden i minutter.
